citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:20p on
27-Feb-20.
ACI Bartels arrived at the facility, rang the doorbell of the residence, and texted the licensees. Contact was made
by text. The licensee stated no one was available that evening.
